headline: A Fresh Look at Medtronic’s (MDT) Valuation Following Strategic Board Changes and Growth Initiatives
summary: If you own shares in Medtronic (MDT) or are curious about adding it to your portfolio, this past week has offered plenty to consider. Medtronic’s agreement with Elliott Investment Management to expand its board, bringing in experienced leaders and creating two new committees focused on growth and operational improvement, suggests the company is sharpening its strategic focus. Coupled with the reiteration of revenue guidance and steady quarterly results, these steps reflect growing urgency...
